description:
Reported via email. I did a search and don't see much cleanup is needed, but here are some specific areas:

- Delete the "Old Docs" section under doc/source/devref/volume.rst that's in http://nova.openstack.org/devref/volume.html
- Clean up doc strings in the nova volume manager that are output to http://nova.openstack.org/2011.2/api/nova.volume.manager.html
title: AOE or ata-over-ethernet references in the docs should be eliminated
